BULLET::::- The Advocate. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.advocate.com/poll_results.asp%3Fid%3D15492"&gt;Advocate.com Poll Results, GLAAD&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Advocate"&gt;The Advocate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 18, 2005 *

</ul>


