BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.opera.com/pressreleases/en/2005/04/19/"&gt;Speed, Security and Simplicity&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AOpera%20Software"&gt;Opera Software&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 19, 2005
