BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200504/s1348166.htm"&gt;Norway whaling season has largest quota in over a decade&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AABC%20News%20Online"&gt;ABC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 20, 2005
