BULLET::::- AP Wire. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.thewmurchannel.com/news/4397598/detail.html"&gt;Maine, N.H. Senators Argue Over Canadian Drugs&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATheWMURChannel.com%20-%20News"&gt;TheWMURChannel.com - News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 21, 2005
