BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.akm.ru/eng/news/2005/april/22/ns1445784.htm"&gt;Hydro started the gas pipeline laying.&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Aakm.ru"&gt;akm.ru&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 22, 2005
