BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//breakingnews.iol.ie/entertainment/story.asp%3Fj%3D140678266%26amp%3Bp%3Dy4x67897z"&gt;U2 to play third Croke Park gig&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AIreland%20Online"&gt;Ireland Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 22, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.rte.ie/arts/2005/0422/u2.html"&gt;U2 set to play third Croke Park date&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARTE%20News"&gt;RTE News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 22, 2005
BULLET::::- Maureen Coleman. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/lifestyle/music/story.jsp%3Fstory%3D632099"&gt;U2 to play third Dublin concert&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Belfast%20Telegraph"&gt;The Belfast Telegraph&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 22, 2005

</ul>


