BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//politics.guardian.co.uk/places/browse/0%2C9354%2C%2C00.html"&gt;Guardian politics &amp;ndash; Ask Aristotle&lt;/a&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/politics/vote_2005/constituencies/default.stm"&gt;BBC Election 2005 results&lt;/a&gt;

</ul>
<h2>The race to declare</h2>
In every General Election there is an informal race amongst the constituencies to declare a result first. 


