BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com./2005/SHOWBIZ/Movies/04/23/johnj.mills.ap/index.html"&gt;Oscar-winner John Mills dead at 97&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 23, 2005

</ul>


