BULLET::::- Donny Jackson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.crmbuyer.com/story/business/qwest-vonage-911-112008P42VCG.xhtml"&gt;Qwest Agrees To Provide Vonage E-911 Access&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACRM%20Buyer"&gt;CRM Buyer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 20, 2005

</ul>
