BULLET::::- Beti Bilandzic. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.swissinfo.org/sen/swissinfo.html%3FsiteSect%3D143%26amp%3Bsid%3D5711811%26amp%3BcKey%3D1114184141000"&gt;Serb General Pavkovic to Surrender to Hague&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASwissInfo"&gt;SwissInfo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 22, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.com/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DworldNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D8266842"&gt;Serb General Pavkovic to Surrender to Hague&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 22, 2005

</ul>


