</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUPI"&gt;UPI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.sciencedaily.com/upi/index.php%3Ffeed%3DScience%26amp%3Barticle%3DUPI-1-20050424-12564500-bc-india-hygiene.xml"&gt;Food stall operators given hygiene tips&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AScienceDaily"&gt;ScienceDaily&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 24, 2005

</ul>
