BULLET::::- Antonia Oprita. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.swissinfo.org/sen/swissinfo.html%3FsiteSect%3D143%26amp%3Bsid%3D5716614%26amp%3BcKey%3D1114365909000"&gt;Romanians want Iraq pullout, poll finds; PM wary&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASwissinfo"&gt;Swissinfo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 24, 2005

