BULLET::::- &lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAgence%20France-Presse"&gt;AFP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.hindustantimes.com/news/181_1337788%2C00050004.htm"&gt;Two dead, 16 hurt in Myanmar market blast: Official&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHindustantimes"&gt;Hindustantimes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 26, 2005

