BULLET::::- Ariel Schalit, Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/04/26/AR2005042601282.html"&gt;Thousands Bid Farewell to Ezer Weizman&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Tuesday, April 26, 2005; 9:12 PM

