BULLET::::- Wire agencies. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.guardian.co.uk/Iraq/Story/0%2C2763%2C1473376%2C00.html"&gt;US soldier to be executed&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGuardian%20Unlimited"&gt;Guardian Unlimited&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 29, 2005
BULLET::::- AP Wire. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/04/29/national/29grenade.html"&gt;Soldier Sentenced to Death for Grenade Attack&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20New%20York%20Times"&gt;The New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 29, 2005
BULLET::::- Steve Esack. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.mcall.com/news/local/all-a1_3akbarapr29%2C0%2C2677757.story%3Fcoll%3Dall-newslocal-hed"&gt;Akbar gets death sentence&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Amcall.com%20-%20Allentown%20PA"&gt;mcall.com - Allentown PA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 29, 2005

