BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.wral.com/news/4440972/detail.html"&gt;Wilmington Man Finds Finger In His Frozen Custard&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWRAL%20Raleigh-Durham"&gt;WRAL Raleigh-Durham&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 2, 2005

</ul>
