BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nbc17.com/news/4437167/detail.html"&gt;Man Says He Found Finger In Frozen Custard&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANBC17%20Raleigh-Durham"&gt;NBC17 Raleigh-Durham&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 2, 2005

