BULLET::::- timothy. "&lt;a href="http%3A//hardware.slashdot.org/article.pl%3Fsid%3D05/05/02/041206"&gt;Sony's Robot Attends Pre-School&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASlashdot"&gt;Slashdot&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 2, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//japantoday.com/e/%3Fcontent%3Dnews%26amp%3Bcat%3D4%26amp%3Bid%3D335992"&gt;Sony's Qrio robot attending nursery school in California&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AJapan%20Today"&gt;Japan Today&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 1, 2005
BULLET::::- Joshua. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.geek.com/news/geeknews/2005May/gee20050503030303.htm"&gt;Robot-toddler interaction study&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGeek.com"&gt;Geek.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 3, 2005

</ul>


