BULLET::::- Somini Sengupta. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/05/05/international/asia/05pakistan.html%3Fhp%26amp%3Bex%3D1115265600%26amp%3Ben%3D2c72988bfadaa147%26amp%3Bei%3D5094%26amp%3Bpartner%3Dhomepage"&gt;Pakistan Reports Arrest of a Senior Qaeda Leader&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20New%20York%20Times"&gt;The New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 5, 2005
