BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.voanews.com/english/2005-05-04-voa32.cfm"&gt;Bush: Arrest in Pakistan Is Critical Victory Against Terrorism&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AVoice%20of%20America"&gt;Voice of America&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 4, 2005
