BULLET::::- Nabi Abdullaev. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.isn.ethz.ch/news/sw/details.cfm%3Fid%3D11227"&gt;Russian nuclear scientist arrested in Switzerland&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AISN"&gt;ISN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 4, 2005
