BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//edition.cnn.com/2005/WORLD/europe/05/04/swiss.russian/"&gt;Swiss arrest Russian ex-minister&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN%20International"&gt;CNN International&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 4, 2005
