BULLET::::- Sean L. McCarthy. "&lt;a href="http%3A//theedge.bostonherald.com/artsNews/view.bg%3Farticleid%3D81319%26amp%3Bformat%3Dtext"&gt;Street theater: Quincy Market signs up summer's worth of sidewalk performers&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABoston%20Herald"&gt;Boston Herald&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 3, 2005

