BULLET::::- Director of Government Communication Office. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.harolddoan.com/modules.php%3Fname%3DNews%26amp%3Bfile%3Darticle%26amp%3Bsid%3D2470"&gt;Cooperation in Research and Development with Finland was the Main Focus of Prime&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHarold%20Doan%20Associates%2C%20Ltd"&gt;Harold Doan Associates, Ltd&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 3 2005
</ul>
 


