BULLET::::- Dale Kasler. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.sacbee.com/content/homes/re_news/story/12345358p-13213074c.html"&gt;Firm says it can make mortgages go away; judge calls it a scam&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Sacramento%20Bee"&gt;The Sacramento Bee&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 15, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cleveland.bbb.org/misc/alertdetl.asp%3FID%3D91"&gt;BBB uncovers national mortgage elimination scheme&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Better%20Business%20Bureau%20of%20Cleveland%20website"&gt;The Better Business Bureau of Cleveland website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 25, 2005

</ul>
