BULLET::::- Jamie McIntyre. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2005/US/05/05/falluja.marine/index.html"&gt;Marine cleared&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 5, 2005
BULLET::::- Simon Jeffery. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.guardian.co.uk/print/0%2C3858%2C5064381-103550%2C00.html"&gt;Colleagues defend suspended marine&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGuardian%20Unlimited"&gt;Guardian Unlimited&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Nov. 16, 2004
BULLET::::- Agence France-Presse. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/news%3Ftmpl%3Dstory%26amp%3Bu%3D/afp/20050505/pl_afp/usiraqmosqueshooting_050505155035"&gt;US marine cleared in 2004 shooting of unarmed Iraqi in Fallujah mosque&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Ayahoonews"&gt;yahoonews&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 5,2005

