BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.instantmessagingplanet.com/feedback.php/http%3A//www.instantmessagingplanet.com/enterprise/article.php/3503186"&gt;Michael Hall&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.instantmessagingplanet.com/enterprise/article.php/3503186"&gt;Tiger Sets Mac Users to Jabbering&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AInstantmessagingplanet.com"&gt;Instantmessagingplanet.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 6, 2005
