BULLET::::- Narasu Rebbapragada. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.pcworld.com/reviews/article/0%2Caid%2C120646%2C00.asp"&gt;First Look: Tiger Lives Up to the Hype&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APC%20World"&gt;PC World&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Friday, April 29, 2005

</ul>


